@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Raturn Policy";
}

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
        background: #f3f3f3;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .page-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .updated {
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    h3 {
        margin-top: 25px;
        color: #222;
    }

    .p55 {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #444;
    }

    ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    hr {
        margin: 30px 0;
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .footer-links {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
    }

        .footer-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #0073e6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

            .footer-links a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
</style>

<div class="container">
    <div class="breadcrumb">
        <span>Home > Raturn Policy</span>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="page-container">

    <div class="updated">Last updated: September 2025</div>

    <hr />

    <h3>1. Overview</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your order,
        you may request a return under the conditions below.
    </p>

    <h3>2. Return Period</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        Items can be returned within 14 days of delivery unless otherwise stated.
    </p>

    <h3>3. Return Conditions</h3>
    <p class="p55">To be eligible for a return, the item must:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Be unused and in original condition</li>
        <li>Include original packaging</li>
        <li>Have proof of purchase</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>4. Non-Returnable Items</h3>
    <p class="p55">The following items cannot be returned:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Digital products</li>
        <li>Gift cards</li>
        <li>Items marked as non-returnable</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>5. Refund Process</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you about the approval or rejection of your refund.
        Approved refunds will be processed within 7–10 business days.
    </p>

    <h3>6. Late or Missing Refunds</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        If you haven’t received a refund yet, first check your bank account.
        Then contact your payment provider. If the issue persists, contact us.
    </p>

    <h3>7. Shipping Costs</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        Shipping costs are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.
    </p>

    <h3>8. Exchanges</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        We only replace items if they are defective or damaged.
    </p>

    <h3>9. Contact Us</h3>
    <p class="p55">
        If you have any questions about returns, contact us:
        <br />
        <strong>Write us:</strong> <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="ContactUs">Contact Us</a>
    </p>

</div>